INSERT INTO `jc_term_taxonomy` VALUES (1,1,'category','',0,0),(2,2,'nav_menu','',0,5),(3,3,'category','It’s another 10pm in your watch. You’re sitting in a dimly lit office on an empty stomach in the company of your dreams. Only they forgot to mention the all-nighters in the contract. Top this up with that environmentally friendly tin can that says, “This wholesome drink will give you the wheels you need to cruise through this night. So go ahead son. Drink up!”\r\n\r\nSadly, we’ve all been there… \r\n\r\nBetter This is what 4 guys wanted in their lives, but couldn’t find on the supermarket shelves. They were in search of a healthier lifestyle without the drama. And that’s when it hit them. There must be more like them. Good, honest, hardworking citizens of DreamVille who deserved something better, since the best out there just wasn’t cutting it. And that’s when they decided to create a drink loaded with functional benefits from natural ingredients minus the extra sugar and preservatives. \r\n\r\nLook, we’re not promising you the world in a bottle but we will say this: Better This is the single most awesome combination of the healthiest fruits with a purpose to give you a better lifestyle choice.',0,4),(4,4,'category','Art and culture',0,5),(5,5,'category','food &amp; travel',0,4),(6,6,'category','science &amp; tech',0,4),(7,7,'category','health &amp; sports',0,4);
